         <div type="translation">
            <ab>The 3rd year, Pauni 27th. Didume daughter of Herakleides has paid to Heron, collector of taxes, through Apollonios the assistant for transport charges of the same year thirty two drachmas, total 32 dr. (Ö) eight drachmas, total 8 dr. (Ö) 8 dr.</ab>
